      "description": "S Crypto Energy Inc. engages in crypto asset, metal, and real estate business in Japan. The company operates through six segments: Nickel Business, Real Estate Business, Education Business, Smart DX Solutions Business, Crypto Asset Business, and Other. The company's products include S pellets anodes, nickel balls anode, plating nickel chips, nickel sulfate, nickel chloride, and P pellets and anode",
